<p>Khloe shared the video of her and Tristan Thompson's daughter True with the caption 'that's my girl lol' as her daughter was seen wiping down the windows of the doll house. </p>

<p>The close knit family spend a lot of time with all their children as they all reside close to each other in the upscale community of Hidden Hills.   </p>

